{"tid":1211783,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[連鎖反應][蝴蝶效應]或者再解釋一下鐵路嘅重要性[請廣傳]","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:56:24.000Z","uid":88263,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"007b8cb3a8913db619d0aaa6eb2c65e2d37577c7","tid":1211783,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"大家回憶一下山竹之後、地鐵4綫訊號故障嘅時候，地面嘅交通係唔會變暢通咗。<br />\n山竹過後有人教想返工嘅話可以選擇喺公司扎營/行路返工/用隨意門。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">冇錯，係可以行路</span><br />\n<br />\n香港嘅世界級鐵路喺繁時係過9成載客率係過9成。以港鐵重鐵部分現有車卡，以每平方米企4人，最多載大約40幾萬人，Worst case 計每個乘客都帶合規格行李嘅話，20萬人會full load。<br />\n假設全香港人都要搭鐵路，又係worst case, 鐵路要35倍運載力先消化到人流。以過去星期日遊行高峰期人數去到100萬為例子，鐵路需要5倍運載力去消化。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">數學題：20/100= 5分之1</span><br />\n<br />\n如果冇咗鐵路消化人流，所有人搭巴士，全香港6000部專營巴士，best case 係載80幾萬人，要9倍嘅運載力去消化，以平時大家咁熱愛返工都會塞車，如果冇咗鐵路只會更塞。所以鐵路對城市嘅重要性係極大。而每塞6分鐘車以2014年資料係會造成28億經濟損失，哩幾年都係通脹，數字只會係上升。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">所以鐵路對現代城市有絕對重要性</span><br />\n<br />\n好多人唔中意玩刺激嘢，問建議點老少咸宜咁遊車河體驗世界級港鐵<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>港島綫</strong></span>，世界級繁忙，世界級服務，見識How it works?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">東鐵綫</span>，1910年通車，本港第三條過百年歷史嘅鐵路，考察歷史。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於其他注意位可以參考下面個post，有合法遊車河介紹，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家注意安全</span></span><br />\n[香港命脈][野餐以外]一星期暢遊港鐵體驗包 [鐵膠推介]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1205357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1205357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f08900ca3cdc5f0d977c616e26a83241c4e82699","tid":1211783,"uid":258973,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1878529/org/8acfbe172c9bab5557b5d17fd51146d2.jpg/Vvwss6wKPGm6CIjw1Urg4MPlfZzW8RaKsyB8p7MgfKc?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1878529%2Forg%2F8acfbe172c9bab5557b5d17fd51146d2.jpg%2FVvwss6wKPGm6CIjw1Urg4MPlfZzW8RaKsyB8p7MgfKc%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=10f88da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181016/_2018101612011747960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181016%2F_2018101612011747960.jpg&h=7b8c5003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔返工人生冇意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3a5fcaa4556287802dd64eb67719f9ddb75f93","tid":1211783,"uid":22894,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:09:50.000Z","msg":"呢個係來自一班鐵膠嘅呼籲<br />\n搭車要摸清楚緊急設備 免得出起事來累人累己<br />\n拿 唔係緊急唔好用呀 一個唔該半個鐘都無車到<br />\n影響大家翻工就麻鳩煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHPEtk5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHPEtk5.png&h=e0650ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zs39Qzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZs39Qzu.png&h=3d5a172e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNetmF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNetmF8.png&h=6a8ffb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0qwjsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0qwjsM.png&h=ddd4ac0a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\